ygData.messageBody:
Happy New Year to all

I'm new to EQ women and love the fact that something like this is out there. Soooo tired of trying to talk EQ talk with guys. Even in the game they speak a different language.

My name is Sue, I am 43 mother of 3 (grown&gone) kids and have been a gameaholic for the better part of 25 years.

I have a lvl 38 Shaman Vah Shir - Nofreesowforu

a lvl 6 Human Warrior - Diixii, and a lvl 9 Cleric - Pletora. All on the Berrel Server. Oh and like all of us I have a "mule" in the Bazaar. Send me a tell and let the killing begin ')
